Deccan Gymkhana, a residential district with colonial-era buildings on wide tree-lined streets, centers on its namesake sports complex, with tennis courts and cricket fields.
  Fergusson College Road and Jangali Maharaj Road are busy strips with international brand stores, indie boutiques, global eateries, and stalls serving local snacks.
